,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-28T13:38:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>當你一無所有就會改<br />\n<br />\n小學嗰陣我脾氣極差，差到得幾個人肯同我做朋友<br />\n到grad前好傷心，個個本畢業冊都好多人寫，得我冇人寫，嗰陣真係好傷心，而且幫我寫嘅人都係話「其實你好好人，不過你脾氣大所以好多人都怕你」<br />\n我就的起心肝改<br />\n之後見返小學同學，佢哋個個都話我唔同曬，依家好好多，仲frd到依家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n依家我少發脾氣，但一發就超大！ 發完又會後悔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  咁算唔算好咗？<br />\n<br />\n可能<del></del>真係要到你一無所有嗰陣，你先識得改。不過希望你盡早覺悟啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你點改<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"494ca7c8be4e981bbaced4aee333992cbda52258","tid":261371,"uid":39065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-28T13:43:13.000Z","msg":"睇黎大家都經歷過一無所有既階段<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申經歷完爬番起身兼睇清身邊既人<br />\n而家仲要有埋女朋友係身邊禁住我啲火<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n不過硬係覺得差條導火線辣著自己既底線<br />\n然後就會爆鑊甘<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/03.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/03.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd7eb4aae34f1ef0154fee2649bb217189b024b0","tid":261371,"uid":114097,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-28T13:45:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}